title: Inner London ( UK ) : population 2011 , by ethnic group
summary: This is a bar chart representing Ethnic Groups in the x axis and Share of population in the y axis.
Ethnic Groups White has the highest Share of population and Gypsy/Traveller/Irish traveller has the lowest Share of population.
The highest Ethnic Groups White has 57.2 more Share of population than the lowest Ethnic Groups Gypsy/Traveller/Irish traveller.

max_summary: This is a bar chart representing Ethnic Groups in the x axis and Share of population in the y axis.
The Share of population is appeared to be the highest at Ethnic Groups White and lowest at Ethnic Groups Gypsy/Traveller/Irish traveller.
Ethnic Groups Black / African / Caribbean / Black British has the second highest value for Share of population.
There is a difference of 57.2 between the maximum Ethnic Groups White and minimum Ethnic Groups Gypsy/Traveller/Irish traveller.

The Ethnic Groups White has the highest Share of population, followed by Black / African / Caribbean / Black British, and Asian / Asian British. Down to the Ethnic Groups Gypsy/Traveller/Irish traveller which is the lowest.
The average Share of population in all 6 Ethnic Groupss is 16.72.
The Share of population is 100.3 if we add up values of all Ethnic Groupss.
